data.description: Spectacular Updated Pool Home Located In the Highly Desirable Melbourne Beach Community Of Riveria Estates! This 4 Bedroom, 3 FULL Bath, 2 Car Garage Split Floor Plan Home Is Picture Perfect! Directly Across From The Indian River & Offering Partial Views From Front Porch! Meticulously Maintained & Fully Updated! Beautiful Landscaping & Oversized Lot! New AC and Ductwork, Windows, Doors & Trim! New Hot Water Heater! New Italian Porcelain Floors! New Kitchen Appliances! Freshly Painted Inside and Out. Beautifully updated Upscale Baths! No Expense Spared- Solid Teak Vanity with Quartz Top. Marble Flooring! Double California Closets! Sparkling Pool with Pavers! Shed! Fruit Trees! Raised Vegetable Garden! Backyard Looks Like A Park! BEAUTIFUL! Community Riverfront Community Dock! The Perfect Location - Walk To Spessard Holland Golf Course, The Beach, Ryckman Park & Fishing Pier, The Library, Shopping & Dining! A+ Schools - Across From Gemini! Easy Access To Mainland, 95 & The Airport
